full_threads.body:
Hi Heath,

I would like 3 new pages created under the "Assisted Living and Accommodation" page of our website (https://royalrehab.com.au/disability-supports-and-accommodation/accommodation/).

The pages are:
  • Supported Independent Living (SIL)
  • Specialised Disability Accommodation (SDA)
  • Respite Services & Short-Term Stays

These pages must be linked through from the Accommodation page where you have the paragraphs for SDA and short-term stays. We will need to create another paragraph for SIL on the Accommodation page.

The format of these pages will be similar to the current Disability links.


It will start off with title, image and then copy (see attached for each), followed by the Accommodation offerings and finally client testimonials.


I also would like an enquiry call-out on the right hand side that directly links to the new Disability Enquiry page.
